data.text: @enews What is so puzzling is what the hell do they really do. Sucks that only their family can be part of this. Marriage is the only way in. The rest of the people in the country should feel a little cheated.

@enews They don’t have access to that money. Most of their fortune is entrusted to them. They are allowed to use the palaces, look at the art etc but are never allowed to sell it. Many titled people in England are asset rich but very cash poor and can’t afford to maintain their estates.
@enews And this fact is disgusting , our country has a lot of flaws , but at least we don't have rich Kings or Queens !
